summary: This is an email forwarding FBI 302 interview reports (likely related to the Epstein investigation) from an FBI agent to a contractor for placement on a shared drive. The email includes attachments of interview PDFs.
keyFacts: An FBI agent forwarded FBI 302 interview reports to a contractor on December 13, 2019.
The email's purpose was to have the contractor place the 302s on a shared drive.
The attachments are multiple PDF files containing interviews, likely related to the Epstein investigation.
The correspondence indicates ongoing investigative work and document management in late 2019.
The sender and recipient names are redacted or obscured in the provided text.
